Enkibooroto e nchetata e nkaji e Nkai


1  Ore apa pee ening ilmang'ati le Yuda o Benchamen nchere ore ilapa yararot oo torrinyunye neshetita enkaji o Laitoriani, Enkai oo Siraeli, 
2   nepuo ninche enetii Serubabel, o lukuny oo nkajijik oo loo menye nejoki ninche, “Nchoo iyiook mateshet tenebo ntae; amu kiserem sii iyiook Enkai inyi anaa eninkoko intae, naa aikipolosaki apa iyiook ninye ebaiki nkolong'i e Esarhadon olaiguanani le Asiria, laa ninye apa oyaua iyiook ene.” 
3  Kake etiaakita ninche Serubabel, o Yeshua o kulie lukuny oo nkajijik oo loo menye te Israel, “Miatata eniporokiki iyiook te nchetata e nkaji e Nkai ang; kake iyiook ake oopeny ooshetaki Olaitoriani, Enkai e Israel, anaa enaitanapa iyiook Olaiguanani Sairos, ilo aiguanani le Parsia.”


4  Ore lelo tung'ana leina kop neitashal iltung'ana le Yuda, neitukuret ninche te nchetata, 
5  neiger ninche ilautarok oogilunore ninche pee eitashal ninche teina kiaas enye, too nkolong'i pooki e nkitoria e Sairos olaiguanani le Parsia, ometabaiki enkitoria e Darias olaiguanani le Parsia.


6   Ore te nkitoria e Ahasero te nkiterunoto e nkitoria enye, neiger ninche enkitang'oroto te nkaraki lelo oo manya Yuda o Yerusalem.


7  Ore apa too nkolong'i e Artaserses, o Bishlam o Mitredat, o Tabeel o lkulikae le ncholuek enye, neigeroki empalai Artaserser olaiguanani le Parsia. Eigeroki apa ina palai te nkutuk e Aramea neibelekenyi. 
8  Ore apa Rehum olkitok le njore o Shimshai ilo aigeroni neiger empalai te nkaraki Yerusalem aigeroki Artaserses ilo aiguanani nejo nji 
9  neitoki Rehum ilo kitok le njore aiger, o Shimshai ilo aigeroni, o lelo kulikae le ncholuek enye, o larishak, o lbalusuni, o lkituaak, o le Parsia, o ltung'ana le Erek, o le Babilon, o ltung'ana le Susa, aa taa ile Elam, 
10  tenebo ilkulikae oreren laa ninche etimirayie olkitok oji Osnapar nepuo aamany nkanas e Samaria, o kulie lo lkerenket otii idia alo olkeju, naa ore taata, 
11  ena entashati eina palai apa nairriwaitie ninche - “Enetii Artaserses olaiguanani: Ore isinkan linono, lelo tung'ana lo lkerenket otii teidia alo olkeju, kirriu enkirorokino. Ore taata, 
12  nchoo eyiolou olaiguanani nchere, ore ilapa Yahudi ooetuo eing'ua enitii, nepuonu enikitii neshomo Yerusalem. Enyaakita aashet enapa anasa kiserut e ntorroni; eidipa ninche isunta neramita ilkitamanyunot. 
13  Nchoo naa taata eyiolou olaiguanani nchere, teneigili aashet ena anasa neidipayu isunta, meitoki ninche aalak kodi; anaa mpisai olpolosie anaa ine nkoitoi, ore mpisai enkitoria nengoroo. 
14  Ore naa enkaraki naa iyie kingarakino, nemeishiaakino iyiook nikiduaaki olaiguanani esulare, enkaraki ena pee kirriwakita olaiguanani olkilikuai aaitayiolo, 
15  pee itum aing'oru enjurrunoto tiatua embuku oo mbaa oo loo papaai lino. Itum iyie tiatua embuku oo mbaa, niyiolou nchere ore ena anasa naa aikiserut, naa enkaitooshoni too laiguanak, o too lkerenketi, netipikaki apa ninye enking'oling'ol ebaiki moitie, enkaraki ena apa pee eitaaki ena anasa olmuaate. 
16  Kintayiolo iyiook olaiguanani nchere, teneigili aashet ena anasa neidipayu isunta enyena, nimintoki aata enipor ilo kerenket otii lido kekun olkeju.”


17  Neirriwaa olaiguanani ewalata ejo: “Enetii Rehum ilo kitok le njore o Shimshai olaigeroni o lkulikae pooki le ncholuek enye ootii Samaria otii olkerenket teidia alo olkeju, airriu enkirorokino. Naa ore taata, 
18  enapa palai nirriwakita iyiook neisumaki aaibalie te dukuya nanu. 
19  Aitayio nanu enkitanapata neitobiraki enjurrunoto, nenotoki nchere ore ena anasa ebaiki apa moitie netudumakine ilaiguanak agilunore, netii enkiser o enkarruoisho atua ninye. 
20  Netii apa ilaiguanak magil Yerusalem, ooitoreishote to lkerenket pooki le lido kekun olkeju, laa ninche apa elaakini kodi o mpisai o lpolosie, o mpisai oo nkoitoi. 
21  Ore enkaraki ina entobira pee elikini kulo tung'ana metapala esiaai, nemeitoki aashet ena anasa, ometaba anaa naitobir enkitanapata. 
22  Naa entodol pee mintololong'ong'o ena bae; kainyoo pee eibulaa enkinyalata pee einyal ilaiguanak?”


23  Ore ake pee eisumi entashati e mpalai o laiguanani Artaserser te dukuya Rehum o Shimshai olaigeroni o lelo le ncholuek enye, neisarrisar aapuo enetii Ilyahudi te Yerusalem ore te nkisikong'ata o te ngolon neitapal ninche esiaai.

Enyaaka esiaai e nkaji e Nkai aiteru


24   Ore ina siaai e nkaji e Nkai natii Yerusalem neitasheyieki; neitashe ometabau olapa liare le nkitoria e Darias olaiguanani le Parsia.

